onest male name of all, and not only among the Normans. In the later Middle Ages it was overtaken by   John  , but continued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"William De Maltbie was born in 1440, in England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 son with Elizabeth Clifford. He died in 1547, in Nottinghamshire, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 107."},"et":{"1440–1547":"1440–1547","1523–1581":"1523–1581","1510–1557":"1510–1557","1547":"1547","1557":"1557","1523":"1523","1510":"1510","1440":"1440","about 1510":"umbes 1510","1581":"1581","Kenbie England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Nottinghamshire, England":"Nottinghamshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1440–1547":"1440–1547","1523–1581":"1523–1581","1510–1557":"1510–1557","1547":"1547","1557":"1557","1523":"1523","1510":"1510","1440":"1440","about 1510":"noin 1510","1581":"1581","Kenbie England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Nottinghamshire, England":"Nottinghamshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1440–1547":"1440–1547","1523–1581":"1523–1581","1510–1557":"1510–1557","1547":"1547","1557":"1557","1523":"1523","1510":"1510","1440":"1440","about 1510":"environ 1510","1581":"1581","Kenbie England":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Nottinghamshire, England":"Nottinghamshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","England":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"William De Maltbie est né en 1440, à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Elizabeth Clifford. Il est décédé en 1547, à Nottinghamshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, à l’âge de 107 ans."},"de":{"1440–1547":"1440–1547","1523–1581":"1523–1581","1510–1557":"1510–1557","1547":"1547","1557":"1557","1523":"1523","1510":"1510","1440":"1440","about 1510":"um 1510","1581":"1581","Kenbie England":"England, United Kingdom","Nottinghamshire, England":"Nottinghamshire, England, Unite